<br>
Gods - supernatural beings or forces exerting a directed control over some aspect of the environment.<br>
<br>
Naturalist - one who believes there is a natural explanation for the world around them that does not allow a supernatual explanation.<br>
<br>
Most of the atheists here (not everywhere, just here) do not believe in a god AND do not believe in the supernatural, but the two positions are not wed.<br>
